Versions

Versions can be viewed from the "Version" tab of any system object.

To review the version click on the header link of the system object. The version will be opened for review. The actions available are Print and Export As.

You can revert to a version by selecting Revert to this Version action.

Compere versions

 

Compare versions action is available for uploaded documents. More than one version of the document should be uploaded.

For uploading new version of a document use Upload New Version button

 

Note: Have in mind that you can compare files in different formats. The first file can be in doc and the second can be in pdf format.

To review the versions of a document open the Versions. Select the versions you want to compare and click on the Compare versions button

 

A comparison file will be download to your computer. Open the file review the compared content. The differences are marked in red.
